00:20:51.121 --> 00:20:52.840
We've done iPad prototypes.

00:20:52.840 --> 00:20:58.250
This is a company called FitStar
that does a mobile fitness app.

00:20:58.250 --> 00:21:05.330
And here we were
actually prototyping--

00:21:05.330 --> 00:21:07.160
