00:21:07.160 --> 00:21:09.980
We were actually
prototyping motion and sound

00:21:09.980 --> 00:21:11.750
on this prototype.

00:21:11.750 --> 00:21:13.450
And so there's
actually video playing,

00:21:13.450 --> 00:21:16.527
and we were recording audio
during the prototyping phase.

00:21:16.527 --> 00:21:18.610
So we were actually
prototyping an audio interface

00:21:18.610 --> 00:21:21.150
where you're stepped back three
or four feet from the iPad,

00:21:21.150 --> 00:21:23.570
and it's giving you
instructions out loud.

00:21:23.570 --> 00:21:27.600
And that was a really
interesting study that we did.

00:21:27.600 --> 00:21:29.910
See if we can get to
the next slide here.

00:21:29.910 --> 00:21:31.480
Maybe if I press it harder.

