00:37:58.140 --> 00:37:59.690
because he observed
what people are

00:37:59.690 --> 00:38:03.090
like when they go to
the store to buy coffee.

00:38:03.090 --> 00:38:05.170
And you want to end
with user research.

00:38:05.170 --> 00:38:06.350
You just created something.

00:38:06.350 --> 00:38:07.940
You finished, closed
Photoshop, or you

00:38:07.940 --> 00:38:09.760
