prototype and coding.

00:38:09.760 --> 00:38:11.634
And now you can bring
that to people and ask,

00:38:11.634 --> 00:38:12.780
is that meeting your goals?

00:38:12.780 --> 00:38:16.300
There's always interesting
things to learn.

00:38:16.300 --> 00:38:17.850
The other hack
around accountability

00:38:17.850 --> 00:38:21.152
is how to optimize
