it and expose it.

00:43:37.646 --> 00:43:39.020
We want to ask
them how it works,

00:43:39.020 --> 00:43:40.920
and make sure that the
way we make decisions

00:43:40.920 --> 00:43:42.780
mirrors that so
that we don't create

00:43:42.780 --> 00:43:44.292
a false sense of collegiality.

00:43:44.292 --> 00:43:46.500
DANIEL BURKA: A lot of the
