00:43:48.340 --> 00:43:50.790
know, we're not standing
around arguing with each other,

00:43:50.790 --> 00:43:53.380
because then the person with
the loudest voice can win.

00:43:53.380 --> 00:43:56.540
We're stopping, doing a
lot of individual thinking,

00:43:56.540 --> 00:43:58.600
and then voting individually.

00:43:58.600 --> 00:44:01.370
So people are much more
independent of each other,

00:44:01.370 --> 00:44:06.130
