00:44:26.080 --> 00:44:28.390
We think that you can
get really good data

00:44:28.390 --> 00:44:29.891
from a lot of different ways.

00:44:29.891 --> 00:44:31.890
And one of them is these
kinds of user research.

00:44:31.890 --> 00:44:33.570
There are other
ways to get it fast.

00:44:33.570 --> 00:44:36.195
And I understand sometimes there
are certain kinds of decisions

00:44:36.195 --> 00:44:38.190
that you can only get
from a real world launch.

00:44:38.190 --> 00:44:41.820
But our framework,
our lens, is what

00:44:41.820 --> 00:44:45.544
