00:44:50.260 --> 00:44:52.200
We need to test it somehow.

00:44:52.200 --> 00:44:54.860
And if we think of it as
a prototype and a test

00:44:54.860 --> 00:44:56.790
it opens up a new
world of possibilities.

00:44:56.790 --> 00:44:58.248
When you think the
only way you can

00:44:58.248 --> 00:45:00.020
get data is to
launch and measure

00:45:00.020 --> 00:45:03.720
a live product, or a fully
functional live product,

00:45:03.720 --> 00:45:04.430
it limits you.

00:45:04.430 --> 00:45:06.150
So without detail
it's hard for me

00:45:06.150 --> 00:45:07.900
to not give that kind
of hand wavy answer,

00:45:07.900 --> 00:45:10.310
but I think the key
for us is always

00:45:10.310 --> 00:45:14.629
thinking what's the fastest
way to answer the unknown.

